dc_title_s: France--west coast, Chaussée de Sein to Belle-Île (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Place names in French with glossary in English. "Copyright 1996 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map no.37360. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Defense Mapping Agency. (1996). France--west coast, Chaussée de Sein to Belle-Île (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/zg848xr0120 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
